<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ChatServer - Secure Self-Hosted Communication Platform</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Deploy your own private communication server with enterprise-grade features. Complete privacy, one-click deployment, and full control over your messaging infrastructure.">
    
    <!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer">
    <meta property="og:title" content="ChatServer - Secure Self-Hosted Communication Platform">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Deploy your own private communication server with enterprise-grade features. Complete privacy, one-click deployment, and full control over your messaging infrastructure.">
    
    <!-- Twitter -->
    <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta property="twitter:url" content="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer">
    <meta property="twitter:title" content="ChatServer - Secure Self-Hosted Communication Platform">
    <meta property="twitter:description" content="Deploy your own private communication server with enterprise-grade features. Complete privacy, one-click deployment, and full control over your messaging infrastructure.">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .header-section {
            margin: 40px auto 20px;
            position: relative;
            min-height: 67vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .header-content {
            display: block;
        }
        
        .header-left {
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .top-nav {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .top-signin-button {
            padding: 6px 16px;
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            height: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .top-signin-button:hover {
            background: #555;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 60px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #112;
            margin-bottom: 120px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }    

        .logo-icon {
            font-size: 53px;
            -webkit-filter: invert(100%);
            filter: invert(100%) brightness(0%);
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        
        .hero-tagline {
            font-size: 58px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #336;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        
        .sub-tagline {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #464669;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .api-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #212529;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .api-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .api-card {
            display: block;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .api-card:hover {
            border-color: #212529;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .api-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #212529;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .api-description {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .simple-footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px auto;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .simple-footer p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .contact-link {
            color: #212529;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .contact-link:hover {
            border-color: #212529;
        }
        
        .github-section {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .github-button {
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            background: transparent;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #212529;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 0px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        
        .github-button:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        
        .github-button svg {
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            fill: #212529;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 15px;
            }
            
            .header-section {
                margin: 20px auto 10px;
                min-height: 60vh;
            }
            
            .api-section {
                margin: 20px auto;
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .logo {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero-tagline {
                font-size: 40px;
                line-height: 1.2;
                letter-spacing: -1px;
            }
            
            .sub-tagline {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .api-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header-section">
            <div class="top-nav">
                <a href="/login" class="top-signin-button">Sign In</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="header-left">
                    <h1 class="logo"><span class="logo-icon">ðŸ’¬</span>#(productName)</h1>
                    <h2 class="hero-tagline">A secure, self-hosted communication platform.</h2>
                    <p class="sub-tagline">Perfect for teams, families, or organizations that prioritize privacy and want full control over their messaging infrastructure.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="api-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">API Documentation</h2>
            <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">Complete API documentation for building client applications:</p>
            
            <div class="api-grid">
                <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer/blob/main/Docs/APIREF-Users.md" class="api-card" target="_blank">
                    <h3 class="api-title">Users API</h3>
                    <p class="api-description">Authentication, profiles, and user management</p>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer/blob/main/Docs/APIREF-Chats.md" class="api-card" target="_blank">
                    <h3 class="api-title">Chats API</h3>
                    <p class="api-description">Messaging and conversation management</p>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer/blob/main/Docs/APIREF-Contacts.md" class="api-card" target="_blank">
                    <h3 class="api-title">Contacts API</h3>
                    <p class="api-description">Contact list and relationship management</p>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer/blob/main/Docs/APIREF-Files.md" class="api-card" target="_blank">
                    <h3 class="api-title">Files API</h3>
                    <p class="api-description">File upload and media handling</p>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer/blob/main/Docs/APIREF-WebSocket.md" class="api-card" target="_blank">
                    <h3 class="api-title">WebSocket API</h3>
                    <p class="api-description">Real-time communication</p>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer/blob/main/Docs/APIREF-JSON.md" class="api-card" target="_blank">
                    <h3 class="api-title">JSON Schemas</h3>
                    <p class="api-description">Data structures and formats</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="github-section">
            <a href="https://github.com/maratal/ChatServer" class="github-button" title="View on GitHub">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
