                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="simple-footer">
            <p>For questions and support: <a href="mailto:my@hopp.network" class="contact-link">my@hopp.network</a></p>
            <p>#(productName) v#(version)</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 Hopp Network. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
